{
  "texts": [
    "Linear regression 55 is a regression model that estimate or forecast the target or dependent variable using independent variables.",
    "Equation (6) shows the relationship between dependent and independent variables.",
    "Each univariate analysis in the linear regression model is used to how much the dependent variable will predict each independent variable.",
    "where Y is the total number of new cases and X1, X2,…, and Xp are p independent.",
    "β0, β1, β2, …, and βp are the intercept and coefficients of the variables, respectively."
  ]
}